"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"2022 is comingâ€¦\\n\\n![](https://cdn.substack.com/image/fetch/w_1100,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fab5d037c-7433-4b3d-9be0-1a62661162f8_294x171.jpeg)\\n\\n2021 had been a wild year in general and especially for web3. You can [check 2021 in a nutshell ](https://alwaysbuzzboy.substack.com/p/2021-kickstarted-innovation).\\n\\nI am going to make some predictions (which of course will go wrong ) for 2022 .\\n\\nSome may turn out , some may not , the magnitude can be different and some very obvious.\\n\\nI think everyone should make predictions as it helps to broaden our imagination.\\n\\nPrediction is imagination Imaginations are wild So , predictions are wild.\\n\\nLetâ€™s dive :\\n\\n* Every country will have its own version of Miami\\n* Something new will arrive after DeFi , NFT ,DAO\\n* Some small countries may embrace bitcoin as legal tender.\\n* Many NFT projects will go to zero.\\n* Some other cool project will flip BAYC. Just like BAYC flipped Cryptopunks and Meebits.\\n* Rise of the crypto influencers.\\n* NFT collection will be a status symbol.(notable in the present also)\\n* Gas prices maynâ€™t decrease but increase.\\n* Every Company will jump into cryptotwitter and say gm . Which will eventually make it boring and some crypto community will make another slang.\\n* Existence would be questioned if you donâ€™t have ens.\\n* Another eth-killer narrative will rise\\n* People who donâ€™t embrace web3 wonâ€™t be criticized by the web3 community but totally ignored.\\n* IP infringement of NFT may take place. And even court hearing may take place.\\n* Information overflow will lead to analysis paralysis.\\n* Crypto/NFT/DAO analysts.\\n* Something wilder than ConstitutionDAO.\\n* Colleges will have web3 courses.\\n* People will dropout to go full time in web3 and will learn from the free material available.\\n* Ad expenditure by many projects will rise.\\n* Increase in digital nomads.\\n* Every pitch will include words â€” community , for creators , ownership .\\n* Zero Knowledge Proof (zkp).\\n\\nThese were some wild predictions.\\n\\nAnd I deserve the right to be wrong.\\n\\nIf you also have some thoughts which may turn out in the near future , feel free to share it .\\n\\nMy purpose will be accomplished if any of you gets inspired by it and build something.\\n\\nThank you for your time.\\n\\nYou can also find me on [Twitter](https://twitter.com/alwaysbuzzboy) .\\n\\nIf you are comfortable in Hindi , [check my YouTube channel](https://t.co/bK8lnwYSD7) .\\n\\nHappy New Year.ðŸŽ‰ðŸŽŠðŸŽ‰\",\"timestamp\":1640276765,\"title\":\"Ooo 2022 : LFGðŸš€\"},\"digest\":\"5rJqswAXSPVNo87a5m9Wtga3sXBTpKBHSKI5jXFmI1Q\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xaef4842A2C6f44ed2D8C4BFf94451126D79A065E\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"2HAoWpy2xkVc7dgZVSBnCZNHqYmqM6Wl9FoN_24qJlw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"_MS_uBzoVpeePKESswckMI_3KkheqBl0qOXv5GuMFpo\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"NAX3s3ykLOxalN8eX-F_I8YzHmOtDXTMWSQQWMQXDuy4hFK_UzOnrKOBzN9VVkTbgLCPtgQH1rzIY29az3L-wA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xe81ffa5fd57d743fadab7d7bbbe6c044b4e5208f7327762da953781bf7c241d53f4d77af45c52396ca79183f91cd280a93e7342ec6c57a9a2a2c1f05416c2eae1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"2HAoWpy2xkVc7dgZVSBnCZNHqYmqM6Wl9FoN_24qJlw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"_MS_uBzoVpeePKESswckMI_3KkheqBl0qOXv5GuMFpo\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"5rJqswAXSPVNo87a5m9Wtga3sXBTpKBHSKI5jXFmI1Q\"}"